[+] Bugs


- [A] Remote SQL Injection

[-] Risk: medium
[-] Requisites: magic_quotes_gpc = off
[-] File affected: dbc.php

This bug allows a guest to inject arbitrary SQL
statments.

...

if (isset($_GET['id'])) {
            $result = mysql_query("SELECT * FROM pages WHERE
id='".$_GET['id']."'");
            return mysql_fetch_assoc($result);

...


